Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:53.54,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,First, I got some chocolate bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:56.54,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Then I chopped it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:24:00.04,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Then I melted it with a water bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:02.21,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,That all went as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:05.34,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,But what shape should I make them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:09.55,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Valentine's Day chocolate for Hizutome-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:13.43,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,A-Am I really ready to give him hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:16.18,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Well... maybe I should use that shape, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:23.61,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,But just giving him his own head \Nwould be annoying to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.61,0:24:29.16,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,And giving him half-naked chocolate \Nmight be a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:30.57,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.12,0:24:35.29,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Oh, Hizutome-kun would eat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:37.91,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,It's definitely way too soon for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:40.88,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,No, no! Don't nibble me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.88,0:24:42.92,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,Y-You're going to start there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.92,0:24:45.51,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,You're filling your mouth? That loudly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:47.63,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,We're both underage!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.18,0:24:50.22,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,No, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.22,0:24:52.51,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I'll need to use a different shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.51,0:24:55.35,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,It's too much for me, emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:24:56.60,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I-In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.64,0:24:59.14,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I'll make it my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.60,0:25:01.19,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.19,0:25:05.11,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I've got myself so confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:07.61,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.87,0:25:17.87,Default,Rei,0,0,0,,I melted it in the water bath, \Nthen reshaped it back into chocolate bars!
